{"tid":639553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"留我做個垃圾 長留戀於雲加","createTime":"2018-04-23T14:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T12:48:20.000Z","uid":43751,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5772c30c25fa8cfc1056d27ea82cf266c6ec1701","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"從沉溺中結疤<br />\n再發芽"},{"pid":"06cb9412cb8d961b5c4ed217457cde9172c274a4","tid":639553,"uid":99700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"長留戀於尹家"},{"pid":"4d726dc5c1f197a7c2d70aa3f79a6cd67982c1f4","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/223643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F223643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eda8bbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法比加斯作客聖西路<br />\n入了兩回合唯一的一球"},{"pid":"57e20d924070aef54e0f2006de8b32fddfafea76","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/223800_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F223800_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fb81986c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亨利效力紅牛 半退休<br />\n其間 短暫加盟阿仙奴<br />\n入替 取得入球<br />\n賽後說：我是一個老人"},{"pid":"e3e6970626c734c559de00fb78c210ee3b3ae280","tid":639553,"uid":153114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27332458eee3f35840eac527718f21e8b77b21af","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/224153_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F224153_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=1c7f47eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加在摩納哥當領隊<br />\n不禁在席上抽煙<br />\n雲加的童年在酒吧渡過<br />\n也曾經賣煙<br />\n說：童年看不穿窗外 因為都佈滿抽煙的人<br />\n<br />\n雲加希望人們明白 <br />\n當領隊 是一件壓力很大的事"},{"pid":"60c8a30a79e9417ebe22aba734444210be16ed50","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/224825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F224825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4af0e078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者因為有個不守份的領隊<br />\n於是有不少不守份的球員<br />\n槍手們 又被稱為煙槍手"},{"pid":"01104e60d9e479203b45b27e571b216447ea68c5","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/225103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F225103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f627f562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他是一個很認真的人<br />\n輸了比賽 憂愁 才會在更衣室抽煙<br />\n<br />\n雲加交代CCC 尼的罪行<br />\nCCC 尼向雲加道歉<br />\n但失去了正選"},{"pid":"96889d8d5b0402c46246e92e2ed45be40b1e86c6","tid":639553,"uid":20197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"109dc1abd338b833b5da983e58e8e1fd5460d231","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230004_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230004_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=65df0b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230009_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230009_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b60c4930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2cf11fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ea614a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基奧特說<br />\n每一隊波都起碼有四五個煙剷<br />\n不必震驚"},{"pid":"2b0664532d4f2d71508fd3066123c464946fcd22","tid":639553,"uid":11861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"support小明"},{"pid":"599882eeeebf874a7dda7ff2c6f4cd8e0078dc31","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230254_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230254_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=9dde73d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對雲加來說<br />\n這是距離歐洲冠軍最近的一天<br />\n失掉了這一個冠軍<br />\n無論將來阿仙奴再風光<br />\n都是阿迷無法彌補的遺憾<br />\n<br />\n無論迷雲反雲<br />\n始終希望雲加能捧起歐洲冠軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14fdb0b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a80c68fa85e412eb0719d590f216fa425716be62","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230804_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230804_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=c393ed15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲加認為 法比加斯是阿仙奴的將來<br />\n也許他自己沒想到<br />\n往後會經歷多年無冠的日子<br />\n將來 已經成為十年前的歷史<br />\n法比加斯離開了英格蘭 又回到英格蘭<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴不敗奪冠的一年 李斯特城降班<br />\n那時雲加沒想過 李城會奪得英超"},{"pid":"9dff60425d1c36a9a3b64e6ec4c29cc141b39ba1","tid":639553,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"被阿迷遺棄 不可怕"},{"pid":"1968aee8c15307604311a850134e734a74270e90","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/231505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F231505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=27cd880e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n列文紅牌<br />\n雲加換出了皮里斯 換入龍門<br />\n<br />\n皮里斯往後說 ：<br />\n那是人生中最失望的一刻<br />\n沒有人希望 在最耀目的舞台 無奈離場<br />\n也沒想過 自己是被放棄的一個"},{"pid":"856416c82833da84091f2113fa860eef04760714","tid":639553,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdc2589b4a542d89ee30bdc8eb480e876f1c3d4","tid":639553,"uid":106675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9dff60425d1c36a9a3b64e6ec4c29cc141b39ba1","tid":639553,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"被阿迷遺棄 不可怕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"被阿記遺棄 不可怕"},{"pid":"7525be2ad3bac309af54986f3d72e6bf0271893d","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/231935_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F231935_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8dc463cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不敗奪冠後的一年<br />\n阿仙奴一敗不起<br />\n最後作客巴拿貝球場<br />\n爆冷贏了皇家馬德里"},{"pid":"4b960121274de58d7da3e63d74227658236ca516","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/232316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F232316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=52dcc3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人說過 黃色戰衣的阿仙奴特別幸運<br />\n<br />\n那時候的阿曼大戰<br />\n是充滿熱情"},{"pid":"c65ebe4843609798da6c482f046b659985f3d875","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"不敗的開始是曼聯<br />\n終結也是曼聯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/232549_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F232549_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8b040bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n敗給曼聯後<br />\n雲加沒有能力重振那不敗的冠軍球隊"},{"pid":"096d204cf07be2c233128f82e944b5854ac70a9c","tid":639553,"uid":90473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1549a566a28c3bee2bd9c461a5d9384c3fb2f79a","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/233255_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F233255_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=35dba3ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在失去碧咸 與 獲得基斯坦奴 之間<br />\n費格遜不能制止雲加"},{"pid":"a19f1a8c3dfb4fe34bf0677a487879a6758143a3","tid":639553,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62198c310fe932260dd5f691ded7915a412f4c14","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/233515_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F233515_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d2a47c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一支球隊倒退 就是另一支球隊掘起<br />\n雲加的華麗 敗給了摩連奴的紀律<br />\n這一年 車路士在三十八場聯賽 只失了十五球<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(初中看洛賓踢車路士<br />\n到今時今日依然有洛賓的存在<br />\n屈指一算 原來洛賓不過比自己年長幾年<br />\n這個球員 好像一開始已經年老<br />\n然後永遠不老的黑山老妖)"},{"pid":"a9755239ad538c54bf4d2534e4afad54ea5684c0","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/234230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F234230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ddfc290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誰有能相信一世一生這膚淺對白<br />\n雲加沒有想過<br />\n有朝一天 會把阿仙奴的支柱領袖 賣給費格遜"},{"pid":"9b6c84ca29a06b73c4e7a983486f9d4b0b306a96","tid":639553,"uid":15935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"小明是阿狗？"},{"pid":"3c1d2d8921371c6b9420e08c0b103d5352370e79","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/234546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F234546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af79ff3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花了一段時間<br />\n雲加似乎找到亨利的代替品<br />\n艾迪巴約不算是技術頂級 也沒有星味<br />\n但配合著年輕的法明尼 伊保 基力治<br />\n以壓迫型的打法 <br />\n為阿仙奴取得了 五分的榜首優勢<br />\n<br />\n雲加認為收成期到了<br />\n高貝利的柏金 龍格堡 亨利時代終結<br />\n應該是猶長球場的年代"},{"pid":"5c7febc32e5aaaa170d5226a83950adaa43d0113","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"艾迪巴約以外<br />\n雲加找到了一名技術型前鋒<br />\n克羅地亞的伊度亞度達施華<br />\n<br />\n經過半季 終於爆發<br />\n金球不斷 有柏金的風範<br />\n奈何 經典的一幕<br />\n震撼了所有阿迷的心<br />\n然後 在五分的優勢下 失去冠軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/000219_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F000219_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=6163f8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這一年 是亨利走後<br />\n雲加最接近成功的一年<br />\n然而 雲加欠缺一種 令球隊走出低潮的能力"},{"pid":"91531c10cc32406a0e1aba4906f2b85705c8d5be","tid":639553,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f16e0c5719f0246bf2aa176176fb7ebd68f2f08","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uyNbE1gn6nI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuyNbE1gn6nI&d=VN1ehRobdsX%2FTtqJnUt3LCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=902afffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uyNbE1gn6nI</a><br />\n<br />\n伊度亞度的入球<br />\n有柏金的影子<br />\n<br />\n阿迷的心總說一句：喔 雲加找到了亨利和柏金之後的前鋒了<br />\n<br />\n那些年的雲加 總有點石成金的能力<br />\n不用買昂貴球員 卻能打出頂級水準<br />\n<br />\n有時不期然會想<br />\n如果雲加沒有買下伊度亞度<br />\n沒有經歷過那斷腳的打擊<br />\n或者阿仙奴不會一沉不起<br />\n那事件 是雲加轉盛為衰的關鍵<br />\n<br />\n如果阿仙奴沒有一沉不起<br />\n可能基斯坦奴也不能順風順水<br />\n<br />\n足球 有時候是悲劇重演"},{"pid":"24a44897e3c340888befbf6d020e05e6a9559296","tid":639553,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1968aee8c15307604311a850134e734a74270e90","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/231505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F231505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=27cd880e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n列文紅牌<br />\n雲加換出了皮里斯 換入龍門<br />\n<br />\n皮里斯往後說 ：<br />\n那是人生中最失望的一刻<br />\n沒有人希望 在最耀目的舞台 無奈離場<br />\n也沒想過 自己是被放棄的一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"This was a stupid idea to replace Pires"},{"pid":"03068ac5553c622c33c39deccf2df9bad62b4e28","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/001842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F001842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9e21313b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏金後的十號 是加拿斯<br />\n伊度亞度斷腳的一場<br />\n阿仙奴的禾確特爆發 入了兩球<br />\n然後又被追和<br />\n<br />\n加拿斯身為隊長<br />\n沒有鼓勵<br />\n反而失控<br />\n先怒罵 後痛哭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/002117_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F002117_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=cc9d6631&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4466aaf3c9ef72464ef16514bb05402716ca802b","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"那時 阿仙奴其實仍在榜首 領先三分<br />\n損失一個球員 不是問題<br />\n雲加最大的責任 是選錯了一個 不喜歡阿仙奴的隊長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/002321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F002321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ef5f7ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張圖片<br />\n告訴了 為什麼費格遜能東山再起<br />\n而雲加不能"},{"pid":"21718371c322a379dab720670af0bf8309885622","tid":639553,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"小明巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d8eba202ff97320e3f860d420e5e4028a699e6","tid":639553,"uid":140411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"好灰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04830f52a860cd2d95f632a1a4ad344ae2c7039","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02499b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=9797e57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2008 2009  <br />\n國之將亡 必有妖孽<br />\n中堅賓在歐聯四強 踢走了法比加斯的入球"},{"pid":"3f7203a228f4f9b79b99244167152bdaa158db18","tid":639553,"uid":30070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"度度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隊自個場輸晒信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9415847e8d475327d7d1c1c6d0b6c5806582f83","tid":639553,"uid":61905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04830f52a860cd2d95f632a1a4ad344ae2c7039","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02499b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=9797e57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2008 2009  <br />\n國之將亡 必有妖孽<br />\n中堅賓在歐聯四強 踢走了法比加斯的入球"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"對邊隊 唔記得"},{"pid":"096804df908736109b5fded440ae1d2d8809c6aa","tid":639553,"uid":57365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9415847e8d475327d7d1c1c6d0b6c5806582f83","tid":639553,"uid":61905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04830f52a860cd2d95f632a1a4ad344ae2c7039","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02499b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F003727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=9797e57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2008 2009  <br />\n國之將亡 必有妖孽<br />\n中堅賓在歐聯四強 踢走了法比加斯的入球"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"對邊隊 唔記得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"張狗果隊"},{"pid":"2c024adfe3c829d33d254097b49b042acbb13103","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/004449_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F004449_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=40aaa3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n艾迪巴約在某比賽後備入替<br />\n打了一堅賓一下<br />\n說：你知道我為什麼要出場嗎？因為你是一篤屎<br />\n<br />\n賽後 艾迪巴約道歉<br />\n而雲加沒有任何懲罰<br />\n艾迪巴約依舊擔任正選"},{"pid":"32a9ddeeaf53ced5130edc571d6729e3ff4a8810","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005255_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005255_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b966fd14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82a22f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005303_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005303_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=abdbff7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005308_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005308_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=66718d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e2f5eb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e39762ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/005433_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F005433_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9deab2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n場內場外<br />\n也是一班好朋友<br />\n雲加的這一條中場線 竟然沒有任何冠軍<br />\n<br />\n然後二人過了巴塞 一人去了米蘭<br />\n留下的路斯基 渡過了幾個失望的球季"},{"pid":"089e94b9bd271efae22a088f90714a6effbcefec","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"白俄羅斯 法國 西班牙  捷克<br />\n多麼浪漫<br />\n多麼浪費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/010008_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F010008_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8dc03e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就是因為這一班人渣<br />\n把雲加應該擁有的新生代摧毀"},{"pid":"4208a1b27493b3ec3f6aedae068066038d753267","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/011300_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F011300_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=43a48119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希比加盟了巴塞隆拿<br />\n雖然雲加不斷挽留<br />\n但希比聽從經理人的意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/011321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F011321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=32b11e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向渡過不成功的季度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/011509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F011509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cfd2bdef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希比外借到伯明翰<br />\n說雲加令自己成為球星<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/011729_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F011729_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8f75f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多年後 阿仙奴作客白俄羅斯<br />\n希比約會了雲加<br />\n說 在阿仙奴的日子很快樂<br />\n而離開阿仙奴 是最後悔的"},{"pid":"5c9e17d638de7da20e547602d9aed22a0a2acfdd","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/012305_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F012305_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c3771718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/012312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F012312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=97bb6a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/012316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F012316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=81072454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就這麼樣<br />\n突然發覺自己已經不年輕了"},{"pid":"cc10d7bbebb1f71a775d776ee0abe089ab378b75","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"不需要 完美得可怕<br />\n太快樂 如何招架"},{"pid":"86f920e0cb90e1d67ce69b53b7eefe4888dff3c8","tid":639553,"uid":75462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9c28aef4ac9c9170e07ec68d6feee351c4a9cf","tid":639553,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d726dc5c1f197a7c2d70aa3f79a6cd67982c1f4","tid":639553,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/223643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F223643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eda8bbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br /